    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Ducking Controversy In Hampton Bays-Flanders</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>T J Harvey letter responds to June 14 article on precise location of Long Island's historic Big Duck (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I cannot believe there is such a furor over the precise location of the Big Duck [''Two Towns Ask, Whose Duck Is It Anyway?'' June 14]. It must be one huge canard.</p>
        <p>T. J. HARVEY  Huntington Station</p>
      </block>
